                      invocationInfo.printMethodReturnType(),
                      printReturnType(),
                      invocationInfo.getMethodName());
          }
      }
  
      private String printReturnType() {
          return value.getClass().getSimpleName();
      }
  
      private Class<?> returnType() {
          return value.getClass();
      }
  
